{"tid":1474390,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"除咗816去銀行攞錢，咪唔記得轉埋MPF","createTime":"2019-08-15T07:03:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-24T06:06:08.000Z","uid":279043,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"cbbe42ce0d6d1943b58f83ba218c5cba5e5ea772","tid":1474390,"uid":279043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T07:03:51.000Z","msg":"見到原來有好多人都想將MPF轉去歐美股票唔做中港股票，但係又因為多戶口唔識點做。我做左少少資料希望可以幫到大家。<br />\n <br />\n1)      需要搵返之前供款戶口<br />\n方法一<br />\n傳真或郵寄表格<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.mpfa.org.hk/tch/main/contact_us/files/Form_PA_SM.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.mpfa.org.hk%2Ftch%2Fmain%2Fcontact_us%2Ffiles%2FForm_PA_SM.pdf&d=%2BEgMKdsH73Wj%2FuX4aBpXdvS0i%2BS8%2FYHgnNJfWlbrK%2Bw%3D&h=14bfa081\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.mpfa.org.hk/tch/main/contact_us/files/Form_PA_SM.pdf</a><br />\n首先下載表格填好表格<br />\n傳真: 將填好既表格連同係身份証副本傳真去3146 7367<br />\n郵寄 : 將填好既表格連同係身份証副本寄去上環干諾道中88號南豐大廈1201-1207室<br />\n以上方法大約兩個星期後積金局會郵寄返個report俾你。<br />\n <br />\n方法二<br />\n網上申請戶口<br />\n去以下網站，申請網上戶口<br />\n<a href=\"https://epa.mpfa.org.hk/mpfa_web/index.html#?lang=tch\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fepa.mpfa.org.hk%2Fmpfa_web%2Findex.html%23%3Flang%3Dtch&d=%2BEgMKdsH73Wj%2FuX4aBpXdvS0i%2BS8%2FYHgnNJfWlbrK%2Bw%3D&h=e2d30bbe\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://epa.mpfa.org.hk/mpfa_web/index.html#?lang=tch</a><br />\n填返自己個人資料，upload返香港身分證及最近三個月內發出的住址證明文件副本（需清楚顯示文件的發出日期）<br />\n一般3個工作天後佢地都會email返個username同password俾係login去睇返自己強積金既戶口記錄。<br />\n <br />\n2)      強積金轉換<br />\n記得係有兩個部i) 已供款部分 ii) 將來供款部分，唔好記得轉一個又唔轉一個呀。<br />\n一般都係上網自己安排，而因為香港有太多強積金公司，以下我只會係咁易例出返部分公司熱線。有咩唔識都要勞煩大家自己打去問下。<br />\n友邦（信託）有限公司2200 6288<br />\n銀聯信託有限公司2298 9800<br />\n交通銀行信託有限公司 2239 5559<br />\n東亞銀行（信託）有限公司2211 1777<br />\n中銀國際英國保誠信託有限公司 2929 3366<br />\n中國人壽信託有限公司 3999 5555<br />\nCititrust Limited 2868 7939<br />\n滙豐機構信託服務（亞洲）有限公司3663 7000<br />\nHSBC Provident Fund Trustee (Hong Kong) Limited 3663 7000<br />\n宏利公積金信託有限公司 2108 1388 / 2108 1313<br />\n信安信託（亞洲）有限公司2827 1233<br />\n加皇信託香港有限公司3183 3183<br />\n永明退休金信託有限公司 3183 1900<br />\n永明信託有限公司 3183 1888<br />\n萬通信託有限公司 2533 5522<br />\n <br />\n最後睇完都唔知點做，直接打去積金局到問。<br />\n2918 0102 --&gt; 選擇言語後按1 --&gt; 0 (直接搵人對話)"},{"pid":"7f229b0745b559036fbaa08392198e9cd24b2201","tid":1474390,"uid":2404,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T07:27:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/84AmgHR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F84AmgHR.jpg&h=7b0503ee&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5c2240876c8b9796b468e741c9f4e3979bf7325f","tid":1474390,"uid":279043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T07:29:04.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"0488fd1ec690f128e3895b3618c21316b22219e0","tid":1474390,"uid":113000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T14:13:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://mfp.mpfa.org.hk/tch/mpp_list.jsp\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmfp.mpfa.org.hk%2Ftch%2Fmpp_list.jsp&d=%2BEgMKdsH73Wj%2FuX4aBpXdvS0i%2BS8%2FYHgnNJfWlbrK%2Bw%3D&h=ce2e1cfb\" target=\"_blank\">https://mfp.mpfa.org.hk/tch/mpp_list.jsp</a><br />\n<br />\n收費比較<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NsfP86F.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNsfP86F.png&h=d313aacf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n最低兩個n/a收費最低<br />\n係0.79% <strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">係0.79%呀</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n選<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">自選美國股票基金</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n唔好選北美股票基金<br />\n<br />\n收費來源<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hsbc.com.hk/zh-hk/mpf/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hsbc.com.hk%2Fzh-hk%2Fmpf%2F&d=%2BEgMKdsH73Wj%2FuX4aBpXdvS0i%2BS8%2FYHgnNJfWlbrK%2Bw%3D&h=f6b4599f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hsbc.com.hk/zh-hk/mpf/</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hsbc.com